.78 to 192.62. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up 1.77 at 379.47.
   On Wednesday the Dow Jones industrial average climbed 27.12
points to 2,678.11.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by more than 2 to 1 on the
NYSE, with 995 up, 467 down and 499 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 159.64 million shares, against 141.93
million in the previous session.
